{
  "stem": "142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were-- I don't know exactly, but the 19-- the 19 Russians, and-- and the Greek guy, you know, they got together, and with the help of sending gold, or sending money there, we used to get to all this from, I think, a manufacturer around-- around there called Union.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "U-N- I- O-N.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were told to-- to get dressed well, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that's the only thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we supposed-- we supposed to-- to cut the tires of anything that was from the SS.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, if we could kill the SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one SS in Crematorium II.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could you [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened is that we went upstairs in our rooms to get better view of what was happening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were watching, but we couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, you know, Crematorium I was-- was calling us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't remember exactly what happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they see-- when they see the fires, you know, they thought that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Crematorium I, they thought that the Germans were killing all of us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what they did, you know, they-- one of the Greeks in Crematorium I says, let's go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's start the uprising.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but-- and they had also the dynamite, and they didn't put the dynamite.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what happened is the Germans, the SS came in, and they kill everybody in Crematorium I.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what happened also is that, you know, the next day, they brought all the corpses of the Crematorium I, and we had to put them, you know, in the ovens.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, just burn them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were surrounded by SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and also, you know, in-- in Crematorium-- Crematorium III, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
